{"tid":370271,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「黃子華」單單呢個名就值得巴絲你入一入黎","createTime":"2017-08-23T02:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T10:16:38.000Z","uid":68676,"like":79,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17ab25fabb421bf679f3cd83c60bb206f46ac825","tid":370271,"uid":68676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/101532_43a8c6b58df284f910ec202163273c08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F101532_43a8c6b58df284f910ec202163273c08.jpg&h=57cec400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日打風 黃子華起6點am po佐條有關惜食堂既片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我睇完就諗起片中啊太太話打風佢地間屋都幾麻煩下 好似要散咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  打風對佢地呢d 階層黎講真係一大困難 <br />\n再睇睇條片惜食堂係每日都為一班長者同低收入家庭提供免費飯 係一件唔容易既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n希望大家放假之餘都關注下呢件事 我唔敢講到捐錢咁偉大 但都希望大家可以起FB share 條link俾更多人知道 <br />\n樓主無能 只係一名讀緊書番pt養自己的學生 但都會捐番200找數 遲下po上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n真係希望大家可以share條片 俾唔到錢唔緊要 關注下分享下都係其中一個方法. <br />\n利申：唔係要呃正評 你地鍾意既負皮我都可以 我目標係希望個post上熱門同埋幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n希望大家重點放在惜食堂 <br />\n大家都一齊化身為正義撚啦 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實開得呢個post我預佐有班人會屌佢地唔抵幫 話可憐之人必有可恨 好簡單一個方法 如果你地呢班人唔鍾意既話 你地負皮上一頁啦 唔洗留言發表架 謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span></span><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/100958_14abe8173c46ea6e31f22cc9a8e1eec8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F100958_14abe8173c46ea6e31f22cc9a8e1eec8.jpg&h=442fa8c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條係fb條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dayowongoffical/videos/1147976565335214/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdayowongoffical%2Fvideos%2F1147976565335214%2F&d=APckT7yvosIwZc4AGUGEJXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=acdfc058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dayowongoffical/videos/1147976565335214/</a><br />\n呢條係捐錢方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foodangel.org.hk/DayoWong2017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foodangel.org.hk%2FDayoWong2017%2F&d=APckT7yvosIwZc4AGUGEJXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c4f234c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foodangel.org.hk/DayoWong2017/</a>"},{"pid":"3b4c62440a0ec1815b98cc66421c787f45ed02ba","tid":370271,"uid":57489,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:17:56.000Z","msg":"無錢不過幫你推下"},{"pid":"edb745402040f0e734ab6b2353bd8c4f6268496a","tid":370271,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:21:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無錢不過幫你推下</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b1480a4c3f725fe68df642246fa37ea3af0f783c","tid":370271,"uid":628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:22:19.000Z","msg":"見係子華BB輕輕一推"},{"pid":"be53c9dc0861b6d670314a17a0217b3d9b1d5b96","tid":370271,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea70c4e2e9fd77109dd6adfea6ab9962eb39f4d","tid":370271,"uid":68676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:25:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見係子華BB輕輕一推</blockquote><br />\n蓮登有愛❤️"},{"pid":"ad1f1423c555873bfdc9310fd9e10e5921e26428","tid":370271,"uid":7192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:25:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ed3f63ff7e444622e511d0b84cc938803b3210e","tid":370271,"uid":68676,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:25:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無錢不過幫你推下</blockquote><br />\n蓮登有愛❤️"},{"pid":"9e161e71adff9d73afe6ff3e37a4e4b68c6e9ba7","tid":3